import React from 'react'
import './assets/css/base/base.css'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch} from "react-router-dom"

import Home from "./paginas/Home"
import Sobre from "./paginas/Sobre"

function App() {

  return (
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <Route exact path='/'>
         <Home/>
        </Route>

        <Route path='/sobre'>
        <Sobre/>
        </Route>
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
